Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, please \Nkeep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. Have \Nyou ever kept a secret?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that keeping a secret \Nis not a nice thing to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I'm not allowed to speak \Nthe truth no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do this for myself \Nand for people who I care about{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and for something I want to protect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla, I completely \Nunderstand how you feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I completely understand. \NI completely understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be someplace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be somewhere {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember how I used to say \NI could make it to the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must have been pretending to be tough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I did was reckless \Nand it never got me anywhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you alone were always beside me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be somewhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can start going forward {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this moment, something will start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light I haven't seen yet is \Nbeaming toward the promised place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started raining hard. Let's go, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to all you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of visitors at our \Npark is increasing drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my way of showing gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew the owner was such a nice person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never can judge people \Nby the way they look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he wants to say
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"build up your stamina, and do a good job."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you're sharp, Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I don't see the Masked Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she was saying that she was \Ngoing to sickle and chain class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sickle and chain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:05.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Resolve Beneath the Mask."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You received a bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's from a fan who doesn't \Nknow you're supposed to be in London now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you enjoying hide-and-seek?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss the six o'clock flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll not make tomorrow afternoon's filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you already looked \Nat the mail I sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Masked Star  shown \Nin the picture is Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla is in the middle of \Na movie shoot in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the attendance at Kaleido \NStage is dropping these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the operation is getting tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I would suggest  that \Nyou not stoop so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sooner or later, you \Nwill find out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, the airplane will arrive \Nat Heathrow Airport in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was wonderful, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check the cut you shot right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in London for business?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I had been thinking about showing \Nup at your movie shoot at least once,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're worried that \Nyour darling only daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might have been mistreated by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please train her without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some guy talking nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying that you're appearing \Nin an amusement park show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...? Yuri Killian?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the nonsense rumors start, \Nthey're proof that you're a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about those.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mr. Dio off today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got Theatrical Camp's \Ndaytime performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have a roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it doesn't matter \Nwhether it rains or shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it keeps raining like \Nthis all day long, perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to have a long-deserved day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have a review meeting \Nand rehearsal for a new performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck! You're a demon for stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss the schedule in detail later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you squeezing your \Nschedule too much because of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing all of this because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle both schedules well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to buy 2,000 \Nadmission tickets per day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about  giving away those tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as presents to the  \Naudience at Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So for the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy 2,000 tickets \Na day for three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which brings us to a \Ntotal of 180,000 tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to purchase \Nthose tickets all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,180,000 tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this  month \Nwill be a rainy month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an owner whose business \Nis affected by the weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this deal is a dream come true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage and my park are \Nbusiness rivals, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this deal come with a catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a simple one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to cancel the \NFreedom Lights' performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're our park's cash cow now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can just give them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without that Masked Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may not come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to hear the movie \Nshoot is going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The success of this movie \Nwill decide your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I selected the \Nproject very carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gathered the best staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the end of next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll finally shoot the big climax scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Masked Star is not there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like Yuri told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is different from  \Nthe contract we signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the fact that the Masked \NStar is not a formal member
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a serious breach of contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... I'm glad Yuri Killian told me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Yuri...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's sunk so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Kaleido Stage is \Nlosing a lot of its audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm afraid that the presence of \NFreedom Lights is getting in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're getting in his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, because of this, I \Nunderstand something well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going back to the life \Nof working part-time again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we still can make it to that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That one"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vancouver World Performance Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the year before last, I \Nparticipated in their exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know. If we get a good reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marine Park's owner  may \Nreconsider firing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prescreening deadline  \Nhas already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with your talents,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they can waive \Nthe prescreening process.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to them and see what they can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to make an enemy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's call everyone and practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reversed Magician: {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the enemy's trap. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to  permit \Ntheir participation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they'd apply for a festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in which I'm participating \Nas special advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're not aware that I'm involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Give them permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, you're saying that Marine Park's \Nshow was cancelled because of Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I researched a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Freedom Lights entered \NVancouver's Performance Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the festival in which my father \Nis supposed to participate as a judge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yuri Killian is also \Ninvolved as a special advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a hunch this will be bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already cancelled the flights between \NSan Francisco and Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.  I'm on \Nyour side, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope filming goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, when is the Vancouver festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This weekend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finally shoot the big climax scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the best partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, there was a new movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A local popular performance team called \N"Z" suddenly entered the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Z," if I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is an amateur street  \Nperformance team. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It seems an amateur team's \Nparticipation is very rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm concerned that \Ntheir scheduled performance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is similar to Freedom Lights' performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, would you mind if I \Nask you to do one more take?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a quick break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I called their office,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they said that their performance \Nwill not be affected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if the number of registrants \Nchanges on the day of performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Z"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An acrobatic Performance Team from Vancouver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contents of their show \Nare exactly the same as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to back out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't give me that scary glare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm part of this festival's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Z" is a group of local street \Nperformers here in Vancouver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scouted them out and suggested \Nthat they participate in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give an opportunity \Nto a talented group of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have confidence  in your performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should have no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, your opponents are amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you will never lose to amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The following is a local street \Nperformance team from Vancouver, "Z"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they copy us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, they improved it a \Nlittle and made it more dynamic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will announce to the mass media{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Freedom Lights copied Z's \Nperformance without permission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then their lives will be over. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like fun. I don't mind doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes well,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will welcome all of you to Kaleido \NStage under special conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we don't want to be restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting wonderful cheers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to be beat by those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now what are we gonna do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will postpone the shoot until next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I expect the best \Nperformance out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the following is \NFreedom Lights from L.A.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Masked Star...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, thank you for the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... What shall we do about the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla Hamilton is not a \Nprofessional performer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, they're disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is supposed to be the \Nday for the climax shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked them to postpone the shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware that I'm selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't just stand by and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I don't understand what \Non earth you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I told myself that I \Nwould never disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:21:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how much my \Nfriends here mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that I still have \Nsomething left to do on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to perform a perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a perfect performance that \Nmakes me fully satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to receive applause that \Nmakes my whole body tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now, I have a partner \Nwho can make it possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not finished my last show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, make sure to \Nfinish the movie shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was my performance today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to run after your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a path we had to  \Ngo down someday anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.19,0:22:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? That's impossible. There is \Nno way you can do that maneuver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, surprisingly, even \NMiss Layla can see Fool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This means... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The legendary great maneuver... \NIt sounds wonderful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, what kind of maneuver is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally, breaking free of the past,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kalos ends his silence and \Nbegins to take action!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The legendary great maneuver; \Nthe details are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The details are! The details are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:23:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, "The \NLegendary Amazing Maneuver."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and \Non towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm here between the sky and the \Nroads, and facing against the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm facing forward so the sorrow \Ndoesn't rain down ever again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came all the way here after \NI jumped over that wall{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are many times when \NI just want to run away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm still here, so, \NI'm not daunted that much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The poem I scribbled down, I can just \Nstart writing over from the beginning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unable to write it well, I'm laughing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
